00757       public static Qualifier GetFullQualifier(ITree fullQualifier)
00758       {
00759          Qualifier ids = new Qualifier();
00760 
00761          if (fullQualifier == null)
00762          {
00763             return ids;
00764          }
00765          for (int i = 0; i < fullQualifier.ChildCount - 1; i++)
00766          {
00767             ids.Add(fullQualifier.GetChild(i).Text);
00768          }
00769 
00770          if (fullQualifier.GetChild(fullQualifier.ChildCount - 1).Text.Equals("ARRAY"))
00771             ids[ids.Count - 1] = ids[ids.Count - 1] + "[]";
00772          else
00773             ids.Add(fullQualifier.GetChild(fullQualifier.ChildCount - 1).Text);
00774 
00775          return ids;
00776       }
